          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", only to snap to our senses thanks to a friend or family member. Unfortunately for Hilton CEO Chris Nassetta he either didn’t have such a person in his life back in the day or he didn’t listen to them. The man recently told Fortune purchasing a ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
